#. Tag: title
#: progressview.docbook:1
#, no-c-format
msgid "Progress"
msgstr "Napredek"

#. Tag: title
#: progressview.docbook:2
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Description</title>"
msgstr "<title>Opis</title>"

#. Tag: sect1
#: progressview.docbook:2
#, no-c-format
msgid "&WORK-IN-PROGRESS;"
msgstr "&WORK-IN-PROGRESS;"

#. Tag: para
#: progressview.docbook:4
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The progress view lists the projects in your portfolio on the left and shows "
"progress information for the selected project on the right."
msgstr ""
"Pogled napredka navaja projekte v vašem portfelju na levi in prikazuje "
"informacije o napredku za izbrani projekt na desni."

#. Tag: para
#: progressview.docbook:21
#, no-c-format
msgid "The tasks are divided into groups dependent on the status of the task:"
msgstr "Naloge so razdeljene v skupine glede na stanje naloge:"

#. Tag: para
#: progressview.docbook:29
#, no-c-format
msgid "Not Started"
msgstr "Ni se začelo"

#. Tag: para
#: progressview.docbook:32
#, no-c-format
msgid "Tasks that should have been started by now."
msgstr "Naloge, ki bi jih zdaj že morali začeti."

#. Tag: para
#: progressview.docbook:37
#, no-c-format
msgid "Running"
msgstr "V teku"

#. Tag: para
#: progressview.docbook:40
#, no-c-format
msgid "Tasks that have been started, but not yet finished."
msgstr "Naloge, ki so bile začete, a še niso dokončane."

#. Tag: para
#: progressview.docbook:45
#, no-c-format
msgid "Finished"
msgstr "Dokončano"

#. Tag: para
#: progressview.docbook:48
#, no-c-format
msgid "Tasks that were finished in this period"
msgstr "Naloge, ki so bile v tem obdobju končane"

#. Tag: para
#: progressview.docbook:53
#, no-c-format
msgid "Next Period"
msgstr "Naslednje obdobje"

#. Tag: para
#: progressview.docbook:56
#, no-c-format
msgid "Tasks that are scheduled to be started in the next period."
msgstr "Naloge, ki so načrtovane za začetek v naslednjem obdobju."

#. Tag: title
#: progressview.docbook:63
#, no-c-format
msgid "Editing data"
msgstr "Urejanje podatkov"

#. Tag: para
#: progressview.docbook:70
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Progress information can be edited in-line or by using the task progress "
"dialog."
msgstr ""
"Podatke o napredku je mogoče urejati neposredno ali v pogovornem oknu "
"napredka naloge."

#. Tag: para
#: progressview.docbook:90
#, no-c-format
msgid "The following columns are displayed as default:"
msgstr "Naslednji stolpci so privzeto prikazani:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: progressview.docbook:97
#, no-c-format
msgid "Column"
msgstr "Stolpec"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: progressview.docbook:98
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Description</guilabel>"
msgstr "<guilabel>Opis</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: progressview.docbook:104
#, no-c-format
msgid "Name"
msgstr "Ime"

#. Tag: para
#: progressview.docbook:107
#, no-c-format
msgid "The name of the task."
msgstr "Ime naloge."

#. Tag: para
#: progressview.docbook:112
#, no-c-format
msgid "Status"
msgstr "Stanje"

#. Tag: para
#: progressview.docbook:115
#, no-c-format
msgid "Task status"
msgstr "Stanje naloge"

#. Tag: para
#: progressview.docbook:120
#, no-c-format
msgid "% Completion"
msgstr "% dokončanja"

#. Tag: para
#: progressview.docbook:123
#, no-c-format
msgid "Task completion"
msgstr "Dokončanje naloge"

#. Tag: para
#: progressview.docbook:128
#, no-c-format
msgid "Planned Effort"
msgstr "Načrtovani napor"

#. Tag: para
#: progressview.docbook:131
#, no-c-format
msgid "The amount of work planned to be used at the end of the current period."
msgstr "Količina dela, načrtovana za uporabo ob koncu tekočega obdobja."

#. Tag: para
#: progressview.docbook:136
#, no-c-format
msgid "Actual Effort"
msgstr "Dejanski napor"

#. Tag: para
#: progressview.docbook:139
#, no-c-format
msgid "The amount of work spent."
msgstr "Količina porabljenega dela."

#. Tag: para
#: progressview.docbook:144
#, no-c-format
msgid "Remaining Effort"
msgstr "Preostali napor"

#. Tag: para
#: progressview.docbook:147
#, no-c-format
msgid "The remaining effort needed to complete the task."
msgstr "Preostali napor potreben za dokončanje naloge."

#. Tag: para
#: progressview.docbook:152
#, no-c-format
msgid "Planned Cost"
msgstr "Načrtovani stroški"

#. Tag: para
#: progressview.docbook:155
#, no-c-format
msgid "The planned cost at the end of the current period."
msgstr "Načrtovani stroški ob koncu tekočega obdobja."

#. Tag: para
#: progressview.docbook:160
#, no-c-format
msgid "Actual Cost"
msgstr "Dejanski stroški"

#. Tag: para
#: progressview.docbook:163
#, no-c-format
msgid "The actual cost incurred."
msgstr "Dejanski nastali stroški."

#. Tag: para
#: progressview.docbook:168
#, no-c-format
msgid "Actual Start"
msgstr "Dejanski začetek"

#. Tag: para
#: progressview.docbook:171
#, no-c-format
msgid "The actual start time of the task."
msgstr "Dejanski začetni čas naloge."

#. Tag: para
#: progressview.docbook:176
#, no-c-format
msgid "Actual Finish"
msgstr "Dejanski zaključek"

#. Tag: para
#: progressview.docbook:179
#, no-c-format
msgid "The actual finish time of the task."
msgstr "Dejanski končni čas naloge."

#. Tag: title
#: progressview.docbook:186
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configuration"
msgstr "Konfiguracija"

#. Tag: para
#: progressview.docbook:187
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Using the context menu, the view can be configured to split / unsplit the "
"tree view or it can be configured using the configure dialog."
msgstr ""
"S kontekstnim menijem lahko pogled konfigurirate tako, da razdeli/razdeli "
"drevesni pogled, ali pa ga konfigurirate v pogovornem oknu za konfiguracijo."

#. Tag: para
#: progressview.docbook:195
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The configure dialog enables you to tailor the amount of information the "
"view displays to fit your needs."
msgstr ""
"Konfiguracijsko pogovorno okno vam omogoča, da količino informacij, ki jih "
"prikaže pogled, prilagodite svojim potrebam."
